Software Bug Tracking System sample application

Requirements
- Allow users to submit bug reports
- Record data about every bug: 
-- Identity of the reporter
-- Date and time when reported
-- Severity (scale to be defined)
-- Description
-- Instructions to reproduce
-- Identity of programmer in charge of fixing
-- Status (allowed statuses to be defined)
-  Allow administrator users to change a bug status
- Send notification emails to interested parties when there is a bug status change  

Components
- Database backend
- GUI front-end (browser)
